Hamble Parish Council

Home

Welcome to Hamble Parish Council's website.

Hamble is more than just an international sailing centre and a visitor attraction for thousands of people annually: it has over 4,500 residents and is home to over 200 local, national and international businesses. The parish council, together with the other stakeholders, works towards improving the quality of life for all who live, work and visit Hamble.

 

What would you like to do today?

I want to...

  • find out more about the Parish Council
  • see meetings information
  • contact the Parish Council
  • become a parish councillor
  • book a function room
  • use the Foreshore
  • find out about parking
  • arrange a burial or memorial
  • book a dinghy space
  • advertise in the Parish Council's magazine​
  • make a comment
  • more...
